Lin Yuexi.

241
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,170
I originally thought you just
innocent-looking.

242
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:35,370
But you are actually so evil-minded.

243
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,600
Since you dared to provoke me,

244
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,940
just wait and see.

245
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:43,720
One day,

246
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,410
I will expose your disguise

247
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:48,570
and let everyone know your evil mind.

